---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 零基础自动驾驶学习系统
description: 从数学、数据与深度学习开始，构建面向自动驾驶数据实习生的可验收学习路线。
permalink: /index.html
bodyClass: portal-body
---
{% from "partials/course-card.njk" import courseCard with context %}
<section class="v2-hero">
  <div class="portal-wrap v2-hero-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">BEGINNER TO EVIDENCE · V2 试点</p>
      <h1>从数学地基开始，走到一次可复查的数据与模型交付</h1>
      <p class="hero-intro">面向完全零基础实习生：先补 Python、线性代数、微积分和概率论，再进入坐标转换、nuScenes、深度学习与自动驾驶工程。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button" href="#learning-path">查看完整路线</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">开始入口诊断</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="hero-card progress-overview" aria-label="当前浏览器学习进度">
      <span class="hero-card-label">当前浏览器</span>
      <strong data-progress-summary>0 / 0 门产物就绪</strong>
      <div class="progress-track" aria-hidden="true"><span data-progress-bar></span></div>
      <a class="continue-link" data-continue-link href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">从数学入口诊断开始 →</a>
      <p>进度只保存在这台设备；作业和导师评价不会写入公开仓库。</p>
    </aside>
  </div>
  <div class="portal-wrap v2-stats" aria-label="课程体系规模">
    <div><strong>{{ curriculum.stages.length }}</strong><span>个学习阶段</span></div>
    <div><strong>{{ curriculum.courses | countStatus('pilot') }}</strong><span>门 V2 试点课程</span></div>
    <div><strong>3</strong><span>门数学核心</span></div>
    <div><strong>1</strong><span>个综合结课项目</span></div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="portal-wrap portal-main">
  <section class="portal-section" id="orientation">
    <div class="section-heading"><p class="section-kicker">先建立学习闭环</p><h2>不是“看完页面”，而是形成能验收的能力</h2><p>每一课都要经过诊断、理解、跟做、独立迁移、留证和导师验收；打开过页面不会自动计为掌握。</p></div>
    <ol class="learning-loop">
      <li><span>1</span><strong>诊断</strong><p>先确认会什么，按缺口补课。</p></li>
      <li><span>2</span><strong>建模</strong><p>说清对象、符号、输入、输出和假设。</p></li>
      <li><span>3</span><strong>跟做</strong><p>手算并复现最小代码实验。</p></li>
      <li><span>4</span><strong>迁移</strong><p>换数据或条件独立完成一次。</p></li>
      <li><span>5</span><strong>留证</strong><p>保存输入、版本、结果、失败样本和边界。</p></li>
    </ol>
  </section>
  <section class="portal-section milestones" id="milestones">
    <div class="section-heading"><p class="section-kicker">分段产生价值</p><h2>不需要学完整条路线才开始做事</h2></div>
    <div class="grid three">
      <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">里程碑 A · 25–40h</span><h3>基础数据协作</h3><p>可以做目录盘点、格式检查、基础统计和结果可视化。</p></article>
      <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">里程碑 B · 80–120h</span><h3>独立数据任务</h3><p>理解坐标、标定与场景切分，完成 nuScenes mini 数据交付。</p></article>
      <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">里程碑 C · 完整核心</span><h3>视觉模型实验</h3><p>能运行小型 PyTorch 训练，解释指标、曲线和失败样本。</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="portal-section" id="learning-path">
    <div class="section-heading"><p class="section-kicker">T 型课程系统</p><h2>核心必修先支撑数据任务，再按方向深入</h2><p>“V2 试点”已按新模板编写；“现有内容”会在后续批次逐课迁移；“待建设”先展示依赖与目标，不伪装成已完成。</p></div>
    <nav class="stage-nav" aria-label="学习阶段快捷导航">{% for stage in curriculum.stages %}<a href="#stage-{{ stage.id }}">{{ stage.code }} {{ stage.title }}</a>{% endfor %}</nav>
    <ol class="stage-list">
      {% for stage in curriculum.stages %}
      {% set stageCourses = curriculum.courses | coursesForStage(stage.id) %}
      <li class="learning-stage" id="stage-{{ stage.id }}">
        <div class="stage-summary"><span class="stage-number">{{ stage.code }}</span><h3>{{ stage.title }}</h3><p>{{ stage.description }}</p><p class="stage-time">建议 {{ stage.effort }}</p><div class="stage-gate"><strong>阶段门：</strong>{{ stage.gate }}</div></div>
        <div class="course-grid">{% for course in stageCourses %}{{ courseCard(course) }}{% endfor %}</div>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>
  <section class="portal-cta" aria-labelledby="start-title">
    <div><p class="section-kicker">第一步只需一小时</p><h2 id="start-title">先诊断，不要从第一页硬啃到底</h2><p>完成数学入口诊断后，再决定是否需要补方程、函数、三角函数和数学符号。</p></div>
    <div class="hero-actions"><a class="button" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">开始诊断</a></div>
  </section>
</div>
